# Changelog

## [0.9.1] - 2020-08-09

### Changed
- color for info-output in logger configurable
- changed color for debug-output from green to blue
- build tests only in the ci-pipeline, but not everytime when running the build-script


## [0.9.0] - 2020-08-03

### Added
- colored logger-output

### Changed
- logger-interface
- methods of binary-files to use references instead of pointer
- return-value of methods to read and write text-file doesn't return a pair anymore


## [0.8.2] - 2020-04-13

### Changed
- update for using libKitsunemimiCommon 0.13.0


## [0.8.1] - 2020-03-29

### Changed
- update requirements
- restructure test-files


## [0.8.0] - 2020-03-28

### Changed
- changed intializing the logger to optionally only write onto console without writing into a file


## [0.7.2] - 2020-03-26

### Changed
- sqlite can now be disable via build-config-flag to make it optional

### Fixed
- writing files in not existing direcotries was fixed


## [0.7.1] - 2020-03-14

### Changed
- update for using libKitsunemimiCommon 0.12.0


## [0.7.0] - 2020-01-17

### Added
- new file-methods

### Changed
- update api of file-methods and text-files


## [0.6.1] - 2019-12-30

### Added
- file-methods for renaming and so on

### Fixed
- fixed build-script


## [0.6.0] - 2019-11-02

### Changed
- renamed repo from `libKitsunePersistence` to `libKitsunemimiPersistence


## [0.5.0] - 2019-10-07

### Changed
- use libKitsuneCommon 0.6.0
- update includes for new style
- made logger easier with simple define-makros


## [0.4.1] - 2019-09-15

### Fixed
- build-script had always used the newest, but not the correct version of libKitsuneCommon


## [0.4.0] - 2019-09-14

### Changed
- update logger-interface for eaiser handling
- unbind data-buffer from the binary-files


## [0.3.0] - 2019-09-08

### Added
- support for sqlite3-database
- simple event logger

### fixed
- updateFileSize-method in binary-files had not updated the number of blocks
- blocksize of binary-files could differ from the data-buffer


## [0.2.1] - 2019-08-27

### Added
- user-documentation

### Changed
- update for using libKitsuneCommon 0.4.x
- update comments in files


## [0.2.0] - 2019-08-17

### Changed
- changed file-names for better readable


## [0.1.0] - 2019-08-03

### Added
- support test-files
- support binary-files
